Class AnnotatorWrapperImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.wcs.annotationservice.AnnotatorWrapperImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AnnotatorWrapper
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AnnotatorWrapperSystemT

    public abstract class AnnotatorWrapperImpl
extends Object
implements AnnotatorWrapper
    Super class encapsulating common functionality across different implementations of the Annotator Module runtime functionality; all implementations supported by the Annotation Modules (SystemT, UIMA, SIRE) inherit from this class.

      • createSpanSchema

        public static com.fasterxml.jackson.module.jsonSchema.JsonSchema createSpanSchema()
        Create a schema for span type.
        Returns:
        JSON representation of the span as follows:
        • begin (mandatory): an Integer representing the span begin offset
        • end (mandatory): an Integer representing the span end offset
        • docref: a String representing the name of the field in the input document record that the span is over; if no such field exists (i.e., the span is over a text object generated by the annotator), this method throws an exception; this field is optional and it is serialized only for spans that are not over the default document fields AnnotationServiceConstants.DOCUMENT_CONTENT_FIELD_NAME or AnnotationServiceConstants.DOCUMENT_TEXT_FIELD_NAME

      • getInstrumentationInfoSchema

        hard-coded instrumentation info schema
